data.title: Deleting Essbase Member Through ODI
data.meta_description: Deleting Essbase Member through ODI - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides steps to delete a member from an Essbase dimension using Oracle Data Integrator (ODI). It describes creating an Essbase and file topology in ODI, generating a mapping between the file and Essbase, and setting up a rule file to delete the specified member when the interface is run. The steps include connecting ODI to the Essbase and file data, generating a mapping between the two, and configuring the interface and rule file to delete the member from Essbase.
